## Critical Product Flows
1. Web user signup/login/profile setup:
- `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/api/AuthApi.js` calls `/common/is_user_exist/`, `/common/send_otp_sms/`, `/common/verify_otp/`, `/common/manage_user_account/`, and profile update endpoints.

2. Package discovery and booking (web):
- Listing/detail modules call `/partner/get_featured_packages/`, `/partner/get_package_short_detail_for_web/`, `/partner/get_package_detail_by_city_and_date/`, `/partner/get_package_detail_by_package_id_for_web/`.
- Booking lifecycle spans `/bookings/create_booking_view/`, `/bookings/check_passport_validity/`, `/bookings/pay_booking_amount_by_transaction_*`, `/bookings/raise_complaint_booking_wise/`, `/bookings/raise_a_request/` and `/api/v1/users/me/bookings/`.

3. Partner/operator onboarding and package lifecycle:
- Admin/Operator auth + company setup consume `/partner/partner_login/`, `/partner/create_partner_profile/`, `/partner/register_as_company/`, `/partner/update_partner_company_profile/`, `/partner/update_company_logo/`, `/partner/get_partner_profile/`.
- Package creation/management consume `/partner/enroll_package_*`, `/partner/get_package_*_by_partner_token/`, `/partner/change_huz_package_status/`, `/partner/get_partner_overall_package_statistics/`.

4. Booking operations and complaint handling (admin/operator):
- `/bookings/get_all_booking_detail_for_partner/`, `/bookings/get_booking_detail_by_booking_number/`, `/bookings/partner_action_for_booking/`, `/bookings/manage_booking_documents/`, `/bookings/manage_booking_airline_details/`, `/bookings/manage_booking_hotel_or_transport_details/`.
- Complaint and rating operations are shared across admin/operator dashboards.

